📸 Interactive Image Gallery

An Interactive and responsive Image Gallery with smooth animations, lightbox effects, and intuitive navigation. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this gallery enhances user experience with a sleek and modern design.

✨ Features

✔️ Lightbox Effect - Click on an image to view it.
✔️ Next & Previous Navigation.
✔️ Smooth Animations - Transitions and effects for an engaging experience.
✔️ Fully Responsive - Works across all devices and screen sizes.

Link: https://interactiveimagegalleryjs.netlify.app/
